-Units of Measure                        
          point or pt -- 1/72 of an inch 
          in or "     -- inches
          ft or '     -- feet
          pc          -- picas, = 12 points, = 1/6 inches
          cm          -- centimeters
          mm          -- milimeters
          cb          -- cubits = 18 inches


