List of [A]miga Key Commands                          
Amiga key commands are activated by pressing both the right mouse button and the corresponding character at the same time.

              [A] N  -- Get new file
              [A] O  -- Open... a file
              [A] S  -- Save as... give name to file
              [A] G  -- Load Graphic
              [A] T  -- Load Text
              [A] P  -- Send current page to printer
              [A] Q  -- Quit/Exit from CÇiÇtÇyÇ ÇDÇeÇsÇkÇ

              [A] E  -- Edit a block of text
              [A] F  -- Format of Text (for one session only)
              [A] X  -- Format of Page (for one session only)
              [A] I  -- Invert Graphic

              [A] ]  -- Bring toolbox to front of window
              [A] [  -- Hide toolbox behind window



